4cb191d7ba6ea49126490d63e16a39cf78623376.query:
INSERT INTO public.subscriber (name, email, external_id) 
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3) 
        ON CONFLICT (external_id) 
        DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, email = EXCLUDED.email, last_login = now();

INSERT INTO location.area(name, county_id)
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST($1::text[], $2::uuid[]) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
